{"tid":1401318,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"拉得一個衝嘅，前線就少一個會衝嘅人","createTime":"2019-08-03T14:35:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T08:08:00.000Z","uid":29021,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"65ab9e39705e0c1b3382a706a0f6633f5d3af80f","tid":1401318,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:35:47.000Z","msg":"你可能會覺得你願意犧牲，或者覺得你自己好醒會走得到<br />\n<br />\n但如果你望下前線嘅人，其實嚟嚟去去都係嗰一批人，可能為數大約千零幾千到（實際未必有咁多），而每一個損失都係<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚多</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>拉得一個衝嘅，前線就少一個會衝嘅人</strong></span>。前前後後有過百個義士俾人拉咗，<strong>假設前線有2000人，我地已經損失咗超過5%嘅兵力！</strong><br />\n<br />\n你可能覺得佢地會保釋得出嚟，但保釋之後要守宵禁令，而且一旦再被捕就一定無得保釋！所以佢地喺保釋期間係唔適宜再上前線嘅！<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你哋每一個人都好重要！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n求下你地，出得嚟就要知所進退，真正做到Be Water；同埋唔好送頭，<strong>不受傷不被捕！</strong>"},{"pid":"8f1dd2a5a8624f06b670cdeb93edb194b8b2d214","tid":1401318,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:36:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09c38db8bb3d355d730cc91a673c771421f63b31","tid":1401318,"uid":226955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:36:58.000Z","msg":"我認為有警察做臥底混入示威者，然後呼籲大家死守，之後防暴警察順理成章拉人，呢個可能性大啲，因為之前示威者入面有鬼已經有前科"},{"pid":"2ab686a5b6caf2db0f1ffac976c1c2c919077f4a","tid":1401318,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"Be Water 真正意思：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1397492/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1397492/</a>"},{"pid":"fe3c2055b113f299d6473dd277eac251f34bfbd3","tid":1401318,"uid":27047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T15:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39748e014aad681bafccc33d9b9edcd4e411ccf1","tid":1401318,"uid":29021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe3c2055b113f299d6473dd277eac251f34bfbd3","tid":1401318,"uid":27047,"li